Hi - I've just started using JMeter 1.8 and found that bug indeed. I commented
one line out of HTTPSampleFull.getPort(), and it seemed to fix the problem...:

	public int getPort()
	{
		int port = getPropertyAsInt(PORT);
		if (port == 0)
		{
		    port = 80;
		    //setPort(port);
		}
		return port;
	}

Hope this might help!...
